data.description: Location! Location! Location!  Home is literally 2 minutes to the casino in Calera!  It has three bedrooms, two bathrooms and a laundry room.  Fur babies will love the fenced yard.  There is new carpet in the bedrooms and new tile flooring in the rest of the house.  There are solar panels to help save on the utility bills.  There is also a security system installed.  Come take a look at your new home!
